high_descs: Turn left and turn right to the dining table.
Pick the pot from the dining table.
Put the pot inside the fridge.
Pick it back and turn left  to the dining table.
Place the pot on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: To place the pot on the dining table.

high_descs: Proceed to the dining table by turning around to the left, turning right, moving forward, and turning right.
Take a pot from the table.
Turn right, move forward and turn right to the fridge.
Open the door, put a pot in the fridge, close the door, and let it sit for a few minutes. Take a pot from the fridge.
Turn around to the left, move forward, and turn left to the dining table.
Place a pot on top right corner of the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Place a freeze pot on the dining table from the table.

high_descs: Turn around move and take right to the table
Take the pot from the table
Turn around and move to fridge
Put the pot into the fridge and get it back
Turn left move then take left to the table
Put the pot on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Get the pot and place it on the table
